history.content:
Hello! Launchathon is back to offer you all another great opportunity to work with startups!

LAUNCH is University of California's leading early stage accelerator. We have 25 startups in our accelerator cohort that are in the middle of our curriculum. At Launch-A-Thon the start-ups will be focusing on design, coding, engineering of their products and many more areas! If you're an undergrad student who wants tangible experience in the start-up world and have skills to offer, than our start-ups would love to work with you. Fill out the application, which includes a resume drop and select some start-ups you are interested in, and we'll match you with a start-up. See the behind the scenes of how a company starts and maybe even get yourself an internship!

Please fill out the application here at this link: https://bit.ly/Launchathon2020.

Deadline: Tuesday, Mar. 10th, 11:59 PM
